<i>♪ If you feel like singing
A song and you want ♪</i>

34:47.710 --> 34:50.588
<i>♪ Other people to sing along ♪</i>

34:50.588 --> 34:57.428
<i>♪ Just sing what you feel
Don't let anyone say
It's wrong ♪</i>

34:59.514 --> 35:03.017
<i>♪ And if you're trying
To paint a picture ♪</i>

35:03.017 --> 35:05.895
<i>♪ But, you're not sure
Which colors belong ♪</i>

35:07.105 --> 35:09.982
<i>♪ Just paint what you see ♪</i>

35:09.982 --> 35:14.028
<i>♪ Don't let anyone say
It's wrong ♪</i>

35:14.028 --> 35:24.497
<i>♪ When there's a light
White light ♪</i>

35:24.497 --> 35:26.165
<i>♪ Inside of you ♪</i>

35:43.182 --> 35:45.059
Is there anything I can do?

35:47.854 --> 35:53.484
Everything my dad
and I ever said,

35:53.484 --> 35:57.238
ever felt,
ever suffered through,

35:57.238 --> 35:59.365
none of it was really ours.

36:03.452 --> 36:05.079
There was something
there, though.

36:08.624 --> 36:10.835
I saw it in his eyes,

36:10.835 --> 36:12.253
just for a second.

36:15.131 --> 36:17.508
I think he can change.

36:20.344 --> 36:22.638
I want to meet
whoever wrote our story

36:22.638 --> 36:24.557
and make them
write us a new one.

36:30.313 --> 36:32.815
I could use the change
of scenery.

36:34.483 --> 36:35.776
Need any help?

36:44.201 --> 36:47.830
<i>♪ There are rules
That I'm meant to break ♪</i>

36:47.830 --> 36:51.542
<i>♪ You could call this
A great mistake ♪</i>

36:51.542 --> 36:54.629
<i>♪ We could always
Play it safe ♪</i>

36:54.629 --> 36:57.214
<i>♪ But that's no fun ♪</i>

36:57.214 --> 37:03.763
<i>♪ We could run ♪</i>

37:13.606 --> 37:16.233
<i>♪ Hold me close
And hold me fast ♪</i>

37:16.233 --> 37:18.527
Thank you, Danny.

37:20.780 --> 37:26.827
<i>♪ Some moments
Meant to last
This ain't one ♪</i>

37:26.827 --> 37:30.581
<i>♪ We could run ♪</i>

37:30.581 --> 37:31.832
Where to?

37:35.294 --> 37:36.545
Cloverton.

37:40.591 --> 37:43.761
<i>♪ We could run ♪</i>

37:48.432 --> 37:52.353
<i>♪ We could run ♪</i>

38:15.376 --> 38:17.003
Immortus will rise.

38:30.474 --> 38:31.559
I did what you asked.

38:33.144 --> 38:34.228
Good.

38:34.228 --> 38:36.897
I need to be the man
I was for Casey.

38:36.897 --> 38:39.025
You're certain Immortus
can help?

38:42.945 --> 38:45.156
Oh, yes.

38:45.156 --> 38:50.286
When Immortus rises,
our pasts will be cleansed.

38:50.286 --> 38:53.122
We'll have everything
we've ever dreamed of.

38:53.122 --> 38:57.251
And I assure you,
Immortus will rise.
